<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n42031c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42031c">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42031c"> 31(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> de mortali</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">2. &ldquo;Eodem modo, Sanchez damnat virum de mortali, qui, in actu copulae, immiterit dignitum in vas praeposterum uxoris; quia, ut ait, in hoc actu adest affectus ad Sodomiam.&rdquo; (Liguori, tom. vi, p. 935.) <font color="green">[Sanchez equally damns these men &ldquo;de mortali&rdquo; who during the act of copulation, bring their dignity into the wrong vessel of their wife; because, as he says, in this act a desire for sodomy is present.]</font> <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) 160</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
